title: Reaction to Patriots Signing Cam Newton
itunes:title: Reaction to Patriots Signing Cam Newton
description:
Bucky Brooks is back with a new episode. He reacts to the news of QB Cam Newton signing with the New England Patriots and looks at Newton's fit with the team, what kind of leader he will be and predictions for the Patriots with their new quarterback.
